Ordered, That there be laid before the House Accounts of the Contingencies Fund, 1982–83, showing:


(1) the Receipts and Payments in connection with the Fund in the year ended the 31st day of March 1983;

(2) the Distribution of the Capital of the Fund at the commencement and close of the year; with the Report of the Comptroller and Auditor General thereon. — [Mr. Donald Thompson.]
